  a) evaluation and acceptance of an ATS provider’ SMS;
  b) evaluation and acceptance of an ATS provider’s safety performance indicators (SPIs); 
  c) continuous surveillance of the ATS provider’ SMS in a safety management environment;
  d) hazard identification and risk management processes and methodologies;
